    />
    <ContentWithImage 
        imgPos="left"
        imgsrc="public/images/electrician-03.webp"
        content="We understand that every customer's needs are unique, and that's why we take a personalized approach to every project. Our friendly and knowledgeable team listens to your requirements and offers tailored solutions that meet your budget and expectations."
        content2="At Canberra Electrical Solutions, we believe in transparent communication, fair pricing, and timely project completion. Whether you need electrical repairs, installations, or maintenance services, you can rely on us for reliability, professionalism, and quality work."
